---
import Layout from '../../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Warangal</h1>
      <div class="flex justify-center my-4">
        <a href="/umeshchandra/career/postings/warangal" class="mx-2 px-4 py-2 bg-gray-200 rounded">Home</a>
        <a href="/umeshchandra/career/postings/warangal/documents" class="mx-2 px-4 py-2 bg-gray-200 rounded">Documents</a>
        <a href="/umeshchandra/career/postings/warangal/jana-jaagruti" class="mx-2 px-4 py-2 bg-gray-200 rounded">Jana Jaagruti</a>
        <a href="/umeshchandra/career/postings/warangal/photos" class="mx-2 px-4 py-2 bg-gray-200 rounded">Photos</a>
      </div>
      <div class="my-5">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Assistant Superintendent of Police (ASP), Warangal (Rural)</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          From October 1992 to October 1994, Umesh Chandra served as the Assistant Superintendent of Police (ASP) in rural Warangal. During this period, he launched the successful public awareness campaign "Jana Jaagruti" to counter the influence of Naxalites in the region. He actively worked against extremist groups and made significant strides in improving the law and order situation.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="my-5">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Officer on Special Duty (OSD), Warangal</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          In February 1995, Umesh Chandra returned to Warangal as an Officer on Special Duty (OSD). In this role, he continued his relentless efforts in apprehending criminals and assisting the public. His work was instrumental in boosting the morale of the police force and strengthening the relationship between the police and the community.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
